examples.en: She wore a very revealing shirt.
examples.ru: На ней была очень откровенная блузка.

examples.en: That skirt is much too revealing.
The article shaded the truth by revealing only one side of the story.

examples.en: He may be prosecuted for revealing secrets about the security agency.

examples.en: Her dress was scanty and revealing.

examples.en: Investigative reporters uncloaked the real estate tycoon, revealing him to be nothing more than a slumlord.
